OL,3,C'I refuse to be scared': MPs discuss
OL,4,Cpersonal safety concerns amid rise in
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe outrage and anger on both sides of
OL,8,Fthe Gaza conflict have spilled over in
OL,9,FBritain and led to some MPs being
OL,10,Fsubjected to abuse and worrying
OL,11,Fthreats. ITV News Deputy Political
OL,12,FEditor Anushka Asthana reports
OL,14,FLabour's Dawn Butler and Tory Tobias
OL,15,FEllwood are both agreed on one thing:
OL,16,Fbeing an MP in 2024 is nothing like
OL,17,Fwhen they first got their respective
OL,18,Fjobs - almost 20 years ago.
