OL,7,FButler describes 2005 as so much
OL,8,Ffreer, when constituents could just
OL,9,Fpop into the office for a chat and
OL,10,Fsurgeries would be open - drop-ins
OL,11,Fthat would stretch over a day.
OL,13,FEllwood says there was the "rough and
OL,14,Ftumble" of political debate, "but I
OL,15,Fdidn't have to look over my shoulder".
OL,17,FDoes he have to look over his shoulder
OL,18,Fnow, I ask?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/17
