OL,3,C'I refuse to be scared': MPs discuss
OL,4,Cpersonal safety concerns amid rise in
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Always, all the time, everywhere I
OL,8,Fgo," he says. "Today is very
OL,9,Fdifferent."
OL,11,FIn the face of a clear rise in risks
OL,12,Ffor MPs, Speaker Lindsay Hoyle is said
OL,13,Fto be considering how to achieve a
OL,14,Fcross-party consensus on how
OL,15,Fpoliticians and parties conduct
OL,16,Fthemselves in an election campaign.
OL,18,FHe is said to be keenly aware of the
OL,19,Frisks to MPs when robust political
OL,20,Fdebate slips over into personalised
OL,21,Fattacks.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/17
