OL,7,FMany are concerned that, in recent
OL,8,Fweeks and months, this pressure has
OL,9,Fintensified, and fear that, too often,
OL,10,Fattempts to influence, argue and
OL,11,Fpersuade MPs are turning into attempts
OL,12,Fto intimidate them.
OL,14,FThe sheer physical risk to MPs has
OL,15,Fbeen apparent for some time. I knew Jo
OL,16,FCox before she became a politician -
OL,17,Fwhen she was a new mum, like me, and a
OL,18,Ffriend.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/17
