OL,4,Cpersonal safety concerns amid rise in
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FWho could have imagined the nightmare
OL,8,Fthat she would face: being killed
OL,9,Foutside her constituency office by a
OL,10,Ffar right extremist. Or later, David
OL,11,FAmess by a Jihadist.
OL,13,FBut still I was surprised by what I
OL,14,Ffound when I spent time with Butler
OL,15,Fand Ellwood, and when my colleague
OL,16,Fspoke to Mike Freer. How is it that
OL,17,Fwe've reached a place when MPs feel
OL,18,Fthis insecure about their safety?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/17
