OL,7,FI've been reporting on politics and
OL,8,Fpolicy since 2003, and have been based
OL,9,Fin Parliament since 2009. The shift
OL,10,Fhas been dramatic.
OL,12,FThis isn't the first time I've looked
OL,13,Finto the question of MPs security, but
OL,14,Fit is the first time that the fears
OL,15,Fhave felt quite so widespread - with
OL,16,Fmore and more MPs carrying personal
OL,17,Falarms, and hiring security to protect
OL,18,Fthem when they have open sessions for
OL,19,Fvoters.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/17
