OL,7,FOne of her staff members - Lee
OL,8,FSkevington - described one incident in
OL,9,Fthe 2019 general election, when he had
OL,10,Fto physically push out a constituent
OL,11,Fshouting for Butler with a golf club.
OL,13,FOutside, he used the club to smash on
OL,14,Fthe window of the constituency office
OL,15,Fthat they have now closed because of
OL,16,Fsecurity fears.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/17
