OL,7,FButler said it made the job less fun
OL,8,Fand would certainly put others off.
OL,9,FShe argued that the role might not be
OL,10,Fright for younger people as it could
OL,11,Fharm their mental health.
OL,13,FShe said: "I have to be aware every
OL,14,Fsecond of every day."
OL,16,FAsked if she was scared, she said: "It
OL,17,Fis scary but I refuse to be scared off
OL,18,Fby them, because that is their
OL,19,Fintention to scare me and silence me."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/17
