OL,7,FShe said she would not think twice
OL,8,Fabout saying something, but was always
OL,9,Fbraced for the abuse when she did make
OL,10,Fa comment.
OL,12,FButler showed us a stream of racist,
OL,13,Fonline abuse, and said her "best
OL,14,Ffriend" - London Mayor Sadiq Khan -
OL,15,Fhad suffered even worse.
OL,17,FThis issue of MP abuse has been
OL,18,Fhighlighted by a number of recent
OL,19,Fevents, including revelations about
OL,20,Fracism aimed at Diane Abbott.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/17
