OL,7,FAnother issue that has shone the light
OL,8,Fon this is the aftermath of the
OL,9,FOctober 7 attacks and protests at
OL,10,FIsrael's fierce retaliation.
OL,12,FOn some occasions, MPs have claimed to
OL,13,Ffeel intimidated, arguing the right to
OL,14,Fprotest and argue and influence
OL,15,Fopinion had slipped into trying to
OL,16,Fintimidate MPs into changing their
OL,17,Fvotes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/17
