OL,7,FEllwood was told by police to stay
OL,8,Faway from his home in a Dorset
OL,9,Fvillage, after dozens of protesters
OL,10,Fshared his address online and then
OL,11,Fturned up.
OL,13,FHe said that even if organisers wanted
OL,14,Fa peaceful protest, they would be
OL,15,Funable to control who turned up.
