OL,7,FMeanwhile, Freer's husband urged him
OL,8,Fto leave politics after death threats
OL,9,Fand an arson attack on his office.
OL,11,FAlthough the arson attacks were not
OL,12,Flinked to political views, he said his
OL,13,Fhusband said he didn't care about the
OL,14,Fmotives, saying: "When you're dead,
OL,15,Fyou're dead."
