OL,3,C'I refuse to be scared': MPs discuss
OL,4,Cpersonal safety concerns amid rise in
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThere are three key things that seem
OL,8,Fto have driven this change: the first
OL,9,Fis an alarming loss of trust in our
OL,10,Fpoliticians, the second is an
OL,11,Fincreasingly divisive politics, and
OL,12,Fthe third is the advent and then
OL,13,Fmassive growth of social media.
OL,15,FI've noticed trust erode slowly over
OL,16,Ftime. There was a hit to trust in
OL,17,Fgovernment after the Iraq war and then
OL,18,Fthe expenses scandal increased
OL,19,Fpressure on individual MPs.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/17
