OL,3,C'I refuse to be scared': MPs discuss
OL,4,Cpersonal safety concerns amid rise in
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FBut trust then spiralled downwards in
OL,8,Fthe years after Brexit, Covid,
OL,9,FPartygate and the mini-budget.
OL,11,FRecently, on ITV's Peston, we had data
OL,12,Fsuggesting only 12% of people believe
OL,13,Fthat politicians will tell the truth.
OL,14,FThat has since fallen to 9%.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G16/17
