OL,7,FThen there is the division of our post-
OL,8,FBrexit, post-Trump world, with its
OL,9,Fextreme elements. It is in that
OL,10,Fcontext that social media has allowed
OL,11,Fsome people to sink into their own
OL,12,Fecho chambers and fire out digital
OL,13,Fabuse behind the privacy of their
OL,14,Fkeyboards.
